You're a gorgeous mixture</i>

35:37.469 --> 35:42.300
<i>Of all that lies
Under the big blue sky</i>

35:43.058 --> 35:44.805
<i>My heart cries</i>

35:44.809 --> 35:46.807
Who's that? She looks familiar.

35:47.062 --> 35:48.729
<i>You're a dazzling eyeful</i>

35:48.730 --> 35:51.433
I featured her before,
in lots of nightclub shows.

35:51.441 --> 35:52.733
I've seen her there.

35:52.734 --> 35:54.686
She'd be good as Zelda's sister.

35:54.694 --> 35:57.443
- That's a good idea.
