35:58.490 --> 36:03.491
<i>There may be blondes and brunettes
That are hard to resist</i>

36:03.495 --> 36:06.619
<i>You surpass them like a queen</i>

36:07.457 --> 36:11.036
<i>You've got those lips
That were meant to be kissed</i>

36:11.086 --> 36:13.960
<i>And you're over sweet 16</i>

36:15.131 --> 36:18.926
<i>Beautiful girl
What a gorgeous creature</i>

36:18.927 --> 36:22.677
