Let me call a preacher</i>

36:22.722 --> 36:24.674
<i>What can I do</i>

36:24.724 --> 36:28.849
<i>But give my heart to you?</i>

36:30.605 --> 36:35.436
<i>A beautiful girl
Is like a great work of art</i>

36:35.485 --> 36:38.655
<i>She's stylish
She's chic</i>

36:39.447 --> 36:43.743
<i>And she also is smart</i>

36:45.954 --> 36:48.782
<i>For lounging in her boudoir</i>

36:48.832 --> 36:52.002
<i>This simple plain pajama</i>

36:53.002 --> 36:56.172
<i>Her cloak is trimmed
with monkey fur</i>

36:56.214 --> 36:58.667
<i>To lend a dash of drama</i>

36:59.968 --> 37:01.670
<i>Anyone for tennis?</i>

37:01.678 --> 37:04.848
<i>Well, this will make them cringe</i>

37:06.349 --> 37:08.597
<i>And you'll knock 'em dead at dinner</i>

37:08.643 --> 37:12.222
<i>If your gown just drips with fringe</i>

37:13.481 --> 37:18.482
