38:16.628 --> 38:19.456
<i>For you I've got a passion</i>

38:19.547 --> 38:22.125
<i>Beautiful girl</i>

38:23.176 --> 38:26.129
<i>You're my queen of fashion</i>

38:26.137 --> 38:28.681
<i>I'm in a whirl</i>

38:30.475 --> 38:31.972
<i>Over</i>

38:32.268 --> 38:37.599
<i>My beautiful girl</i>

38:46.658 --> 38:48.575
